name: OKR brainstorming template
description:
This is a collaborative template to brainstorm altogether about our next OKRs. We use this file prior to detail our individual OKRs.

We can see and get inspired by what others plan, we can connect related projects and get a complete overview.

All these components are built with auto-layout and will adapt to your contents.

By default the system is set for a maximum of 6 participants!

Any feedback or request? Contact us in the comments below. :)
